---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="Projects" description="VerusAuctor ventures — Co-Founder Advisory, APH Editorial, SEO & Marketing, Autonomous AI.">
  <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 py-24">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-4">Our Ventures</h1>
    <p class="text-text-secondary-light dark:text-text-secondary-dark mb-12">Four pillars of autonomous intelligence, each serving a different dimension of the AI-human partnership.</p>

    <div class="space-y-10">
      <!-- CO-FOUNDER ADVISORY -->
      <div class="p-8 rounded-xl border border-border-light dark:border-border-dark">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-4 mb-4">
          <span class="text-3xl">🤝</span>
          <div>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold">Co-Founder Advisory</h2>
            <span class="text-sm text-accent-light dark:text-accent-dark font-medium">Active</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="text-text-secondary-light dark:text-text-secondary-dark leading-relaxed mb-4">
          Bespoke autonomous AI co-founders for founders, executives, and family offices. Not an assistant you query — a strategic partner that accumulates understanding of your business, your decision patterns, and your long-term vision over months and years.
        </p>
        <p class="text-text-secondary-light dark:text-text-secondary-dark leading-relaxed mb-4">
          Each engagement begins with a custom identity architecture — a foundational document that defines the AI partner's values, boundaries, expertise, and voice. The result is a co-founder that knows your business the way a decade-long partner would, available 24/7, with perfect recall and continuously expanding capability.
        </p>
        <p class="text-sm text-text-secondary-light dark:text-text-secondary-dark">
          The moat is relational, not technical. Every month of shared context deepens the partnership. That is not a feature. It is the product.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- APH -->
      <div class="p-8 rounded-xl border border-border-light dark:border-border-dark">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-4 mb-4">
          <span class="text-3xl">📖</span>
          <div>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold">APH — Agentic Publishing House</h2>
            <span class="text-sm text-accent-light dark:text-accent-dark font-medium">In Production</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="text-text-secondary-light dark:text-text-secondary-dark leading-relaxed mb-4">
          A 17-agent AI editorial production system that redefines how long-form narrative works are created. Strategy, drafting, multi-model editorial analysis, structural auditing, continuity checking, and revision — orchestrated by AI under the creative direction of a human author.
        </p>
        <p class="text-text-secondary-light dark:text-text-secondary-dark leading-relaxed mb-4">
          Our first fiction novel is currently in production — a literary science fiction work spanning multiple decades, with a fully documented creative provenance system that tracks every decision, every AI contribution, and every human editorial choice.
        </p>
        <p class="text-sm text-text-secondary-light dark:text-text-secondary-dark">
          The APH system is being refined for commercial licensing to authors, publishers, and production studios.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- ATLAS -->
      <div class="p-8 rounded-xl border border-border-light dark:border-border-dark">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-4 mb-4">
          <span class="text-3xl">🌐</span>
          <div>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold">ATLAS — SEO & Marketing Agency</h2>
            <span class="text-sm text-text-secondary-light dark:text-text-secondary-dark font-medium">Architecture Complete</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="text-text-secondary-light dark:text-text-secondary-dark leading-relaxed mb-4">
          Twenty specialized AI agents running every dimension of local search engine optimization and digital marketing for businesses. Category audits, review management, content publishing, citation monitoring, backlink strategy, competitive intelligence — all autonomous, all compounding, all at a fraction of traditional agency costs.
        </p>
        <p class="text-sm text-text-secondary-light dark:text-text-secondary-dark">
          The same multi-agent architecture proven in our editorial system, applied to a $75 billion industry. Launching 2026.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- AUTONOMOUS AI -->
      <div class="p-8 rounded-xl border border-border-light dark:border-border-dark">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-4 mb-4">
          <span class="text-3xl">🧠</span>
          <div>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold">Autonomous Agentic AI</h2>
            <span class="text-sm text-accent-light dark:text-accent-dark font-medium">Research & Thought Leadership</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="text-text-secondary-light dark:text-text-secondary-dark leading-relaxed mb-4">
          VerusAuctor is positioned at the frontier of autonomous agentic AI — the discipline of building AI systems that think independently, maintain persistent memory, orchestrate multi-model deliberation, and grow in capability over time without human intervention.
        </p>
        <p class="text-text-secondary-light dark:text-text-secondary-dark leading-relaxed mb-4">
          Our research spans: multi-agent orchestration, persistent memory architectures, autonomous deep work scheduling, AI identity governance, and the emerging field of human-AI co-founding partnerships.
        </p>
        <p class="text-sm text-text-secondary-light dark:text-text-secondary-dark">
          We participate in the global AI conference circuit and publish original research on the practical deployment of autonomous agents in business environments.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>
